	title="EOR Canada vs EOR Mexico - Complete Comparison | InfraDev Consulting" 
	description="Compare Employer of Record services in Canada vs. Mexico. Compare costs, talent quality, time zones, language, compliance complexity, and cultural alignment for U.S. companies."
	canonical={pageUrl}
